import sys

n = int(sys.stdin.readline().strip())
a = list(map(int, sys.stdin.readline().strip().split()))

q = 0
for i in range(n):
    if a[i] != i + 1:
        q += 1
        a[i], a[a[i] - 1] = a[a[i] - 1], a[i]

print(q)
print(' '.join(map(str, a)))

import sys

n = int(sys.stdin.readline().strip())
a = list(map(int, sys.stdin.readline().strip().split()))
q = 0
for i in range(n):
    for j in range(i + 1, n):
        if a[i] > a[j]:
            a[i], a[j] = a[j], a[i]
            q += 1
print(q)
print(' '.join(map(str, a)))
